{"title":"Leetcode第11题：盛最多水的容器","slug":"2019091101","date":"2019-09-11T10:59:23.000Z","updated":"2019-09-11T11:12:21.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019091101.json","excerpt":"题目给定 n 个非负整数 a1，a2，…，an，每个数代表坐标中的一个点 (i, ai) 。在坐标内画 n 条垂直线，垂直线 i 的两个端点分别为 (i, ai) 和 (i, 0)。找出其中的两条线，使得它们与 x 轴共同构成的容器可以容纳最多的水。说明： 你不能倾斜容器，且 n 的值至少为 2。 [Figure] ","covers":["https://aliyun-lc-upload.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/aliyun-lc-upload/uploads/2018/07/25/question_11.jpg","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H2f5da7f61b5645d2a60313fb11024c91b.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H3f3ec1c3a9004c11809479fb7440cab0G.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h2><p>给定 n 个非负整数 a1，a2，…，an，每个数代表坐标中的一个点 (i, ai) 。在坐标内画 n 条垂直线，垂直线 i 的两个端点分别为 (i, ai) 和 (i, 0)。找出其中的两条线，使得它们与 x 轴共同构成的容器可以容纳最多的水。</p>\n<p><strong>说明：</strong> 你不能倾斜容器，且 n 的值至少为 2。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://aliyun-lc-upload.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/aliyun-lc-upload/uploads/2018/07/25/question_11.jpg\"></p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>图中垂直线代表输入数组 [1,8,6,2,5,4,8,3,7]。在此情况下，容器能够容纳水（表示为蓝色部分）的最大值为 49。</p>\n<h2 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h2><blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,8,6,2,5,4,8,3,7]<br><strong>输出:</strong> 49</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><pre><code><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">maxArea</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] height)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> max=Integer.MIN_VALUE;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;height.length-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>;j&lt;height.length;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a=height[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b=height[j];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> tmp=a &lt; b ?a:b;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> v=tmp*(j-i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(max&lt;v)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    max=v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> max;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H2f5da7f61b5645d2a60313fb11024c91b.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>该题目难度一般，做的比较放松，所以没有考虑时间和内存消耗，强行两层for循环对比每次可以盛水的面积取出最大值，直接返回，即为正确答案。<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H3f3ec1c3a9004c11809479fb7440cab0G.png\"></p>\n","more":"<p>图中垂直线代表输入数组 [1,8,6,2,5,4,8,3,7]。在此情况下，容器能够容纳水（表示为蓝色部分）的最大值为 49。</p>\n<h2 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h2><blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,8,6,2,5,4,8,3,7]<br><strong>输出:</strong> 49</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><pre><code><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">maxArea</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] height)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> max=Integer.MIN_VALUE;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;height.length-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>;j&lt;height.length;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a=height[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b=height[j];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> tmp=a &lt; b ?a:b;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> v=tmp*(j-i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(max&lt;v)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    max=v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> max;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H2f5da7f61b5645d2a60313fb11024c91b.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>该题目难度一般，做的比较放松，所以没有考虑时间和内存消耗，强行两层for循环对比每次可以盛水的面积取出最大值，直接返回，即为正确答案。<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H3f3ec1c3a9004c11809479fb7440cab0G.png\"></p>","categories":[{"name":"开发","path":"api/categories/开发.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JAVA","path":"api/tags/JAVA.json"},{"name":"算法","path":"api/tags/算法.json"}]}